#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid ""
"We are still in the process of getting the contract signed for the Access "
"Innovation Prize."
msgstr "هنوز در روند امضاء کردن قراردادهای Access Innovation Prize هستیم."

#. type: Bullet: '- '
